1) Set up environment (eg Model name is XRay)

$ cd public_html
$ python3 -m venv XRay
$ source XRay/bin/activate

2) Install dependencies
$ pip install torch torchvision --index-url https://download.pytorch.org/whl/cpu
$ pip install transformers

3) Download trained model files into a folder
  Update the model directory in /etc/web-api/XRay/script.py



